This one comes from my Grandfather, it's a basic Salsa Verde with a Simple Rule, when in double add 2!
This recepe makes roughly 1 Jar of Salsa Verde for more just increase the ratios 

Ingredients 

6-8 Tommatillos 
2 Jalapenos 
2 Garlic Cloves
2 Anahiem Peppers 
2 Limes 
Cilantro 
*Other Peppers can be added or substetuted such as Hatch Chilles, Pablanoes, 
